dialogue.name: Yvyteph Enthusiasm
lines: *mad enthusiasm* Hooray, well don- Oh. She's dead. Well, we had fun anyway. I'll hoover up her soul; I'm sure she'll be a fun ghost.

dialogue.name: Qyvnily Lament
lines: Aw, I liked her. I think I have a pretty good idea of how to girl now, so I may be an asset to Molly. Anyway. Time for incarnation!
